message.entry: OBJ must be an interface object.
OBJ must be a 1-by-1 interface object.
The third input argument must be a character vector or string.
FORMAT must be a character vector or string.
CMD must be a character vector or string.

FPRINTF cannot be called. The FlowControl property is set to ''hardware'' and the Clear To Send (CTS) pin is high. This condition indicates that the serial device might not be on, might not be connected, or does not use hardware handshaking.
Data written contains elements greater than one byte which may lead to unexpected behavior.
